License:
	GPLv3 or later

Building Dependency:
	CMake >= 2.6:
		http://www.cmake.org/
	Qt toolkit >= 4.5:
		http://qt.nokia.com/
	Single Application (Qt Solutions):
		http://qt.nokia.com/products/appdev/add-on-products/catalog/4/Utilities/qtsingleapplication/

Toolchain:
	Unix-like:
		g++ >= 4
	Windows (XP or Vista or 7):
		Visual C++ >= Express 2005

How to Build:
	Unix-like:
		$ mkdir build
		$ cd build
		$ cmake .. -DCMAKE_BUILD_TYPE=Release
		$ make -j3
	Windows:
		Please use cmake-gui to configure and generate VC solution file

